@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_uthdoq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin((v0 + 0.74 * v2 + 0.23)))
    v2 = (0.04 - wp.sin(v0))
    v2 = 0.78
    v0 = 0.14
    v2 = wp.sin(0.24)
    tmp = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.91) * wp.sin(v1 + 0.73)) / (0.50 * wp.exp(tmp + 0.51)))
    v1 = wp.sin((tmp * 0.73))
    tmp = (wp.cos(v0) / (wp.abs(v1 + 0.10) * v0))
    data[tid] = v0
